Name: mediaserver
Description: Mediaserver used as backend for MediaCenter application, longer description in my diploma thesis.
Author: Daniel Kucera

--- INSTALLATION --- 

1. copy this folder somewhere to webserver
2. import mediaserver.sql to database
3. create database user and allow him all operations on mediaserver table
4. copy config.php.sample to config.php and edit according to your database settings
5. edit url in MediaCenter application in MediaCenter.class to match your server
6. recompile MediaCenter application
